{
  "stem": "13395.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- what was difficult living in Germany was that you had the Brownshirts, who really were the SR, which were on the loose.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whenever they, you know, saw Jews in the street, they would harass them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was, at that time not, yet state-orchestrated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would always look at them as a bunch of hoodlums rather than anything that was state-orchestrated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And maybe the German Jews lived in a land of-- of-- of dreams, you know, and didn't realize that what they thought was a work of-- or action of hoodlums, that it actually was state-orchestrated.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we are German Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We fought for this country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We are decorated as German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have made contribution to this Country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We're German citizens.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And by the way, Hitler is not going to last too long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's-- that's all I remember of conversations in-- when we visited our relatives.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said before, my-- I went for my religious education and lessons to-- across the border to Hindenburg.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes when the weather wasn't that great, my father would take me and visit relatives while I had my lesson and take me back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'll never forget the day-- night of November.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father took me, and we come close to the synagogue, and I smelled smoke.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought there is somewhere a house on fire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as we came to the synagogue, we realized that the synagogue was burning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a rainy day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A typical November day where the leaves were already-- had fallen on the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
